data.description:
Fort Lauderdale Water Taxi has been an icon in South Florida for over 30 years, offering year-round service, private charters, venue options, and special event transportation. Based in the Yachting Capital of the World, Fort Lauderdale, Water Taxi has the largest passenger fleet in South Florida.

Known as the “Venice of America,” Fort Lauderdale is best explored from the water. Our narrated excursions provide historical insights and fun facts about the city's attractions, including mansions and mega yachts. With 20 stops in Fort Lauderdale and one in Hollywood at the Margaritaville Hollywood Beach Resort, Water Taxi offers a unique way to see the city. We also operate a complimentary Water Trolley, supported by the City of Fort Lauderdale, with 8 stops along the River Route. 

Cruise & Save: Over 60 partners across 20 stops—each one offering unique ways to save during your visit, and all of which enhance your time with Water Taxi. Each trip is a new experience, especially when you enhance your tours with our Cruise & Save program. Show your Water Taxi pass at any of these places for discounts on food, drinks, rentals, and more!
